      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA documentation must demonstrate version control, regression testing, and traceable change history for all simulation software used in the ensemble.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys 2022 R2, DePuy Synthes internal solver) are governed by validated SQA plans. Version control via Git with tagged releases; regression test suites executed at each release; change logs auditable. Achieved level 3 exceeds required level 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
